node.text:
Ai and Aiko (@aiandaiko) are the cutest buddies who remind us that everything is going to be okay, even during the unknown times. Follow them (@aiandaiko) and be part of their journey. Tag a friend to share the love.

#aiandaiko #lovecanhappenanywhere
